Package com.credenceid.biometrics

Interface Biometrics.EPassportReaderStatusListener

  • Enclosing interface:
    Biometrics
    public static interface Biometrics.EPassportReaderStatusListener
    Interface definition for callbacks to be invoked when a request to Biometrics.ePassportOpenCommand(EPassportReaderStatusListener epReaderStatusListener) returns with results.

        Invoked when EPassport sensor opening operation returns with results.

      • onEPassportReaderClosed

        void onEPassportReaderClosed​(Biometrics.ResultCode resultCode,
                             Biometrics.CloseReasonCode closeReason)
        Parameters:
        resultCode - returns Biometrics.ResultCode.OK if the close was successful otherwise Biometrics.ResultCode.FAIL happens when a close has failed or permissions have not been granted
        closeReason - if Biometrics.CloseReasonCode.NORMAL, ePassport reader was closed normally as a result of calling Biometrics.closeMRZ()

        if Biometrics.CloseReasonCode.TIMEOUT, closed due to inactivity

        if Biometrics.CloseReasonCode.SCREEN_OFF, closed due to screen off

        if Biometrics.CloseReasonCode.SYSTEM_OFF, closed due to system off, which can either occur from device being shutdown or Biometrics.finalizeBiometrics(boolean) being called w/ boolean of true
